{"tid":2395901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重溫2014年] 大陸人雨傘篤大肚婆個肚獲致其入院獲愛國法官輕判罰一千","createTime":"2021-02-05T08:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T18:17:46.000Z","uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"668bfbde9cdc1b171a5bc1961422cdf54712a405","tid":2395901,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:00:44.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】內地女保險客戶服務經理來港排隊交保費時打尖，一名懷有六個月身孕的女士不值其行為，與該內地女爭執，並用手機拍片。內地女竟心生不忿用雨傘戳孕婦腹部，令孕婦一度因腹痛送院，幸其後無大礙。內地女昨承認一項普通襲擊罪，暫委裁判官水佳麗斥內地女打尖的行為令港人感冒犯，但孕婦拍攝她亦屬冒犯行為，終輕判內地女罰款1,000元。<br />\n記者：林綺琪<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m9gJCIt7kSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dm9gJCIt7kSw&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=5c846a85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m9gJCIt7kSw</a>"},{"pid":"fd290dfd3949001f26e65f9c9476c1430081d795","tid":2395901,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"今天<br />\n大律師公會主席夏博義仍指香港法官好專業,否認有司法不公<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">次撚次中國人打香港人就輕判<br />\n香港人打中國人,共鬼法庭完全唔睇原因就重判</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MjnYtvM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjnYtvM.jpg&h=9b429b3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5b5535de748333e60dd89ab45a7874b21ff7a41","tid":2395901,"uid":123774,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:06:08.000Z","msg":"黨報話香港人移民做二等公民<br />\n點都好過響香港狗都不如<br />\n自己一分一毫賺錢納稅 <br />\n但要養蝗蟲養班賤種賣港賊<br />\n<br />\n支那人呢啲侵略者永遠係豁免人士<br />\n大爺咁消費 傷害香港人"},{"pid":"ed6d5292e0f9065e123dda3f5829bac55c48c6d5","tid":2395901,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"434bbaaaf34887cf01831b5496d7fab94dd9da6e","tid":2395901,"uid":178574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:09:28.000Z","msg":"$1000？？？"},{"pid":"aea1a25d36b928fa0b73c793